text: HNE may refer to: * Hne, a Burmese musical instrument * 4-Hydroxynonenal, produced by lipid peroxidation * Chhattisgarhi language, spoken in India * Hexanitroethane, an oxidizer * Historic New England, an American historical society * Home News Enterprises, an American publisher * Michel Hne, New Caledonian football player * Neutrophil elastase * Harwich and North Essex, a UK Parliamentary Constituency
title: HNE
